      <title>新手必看！OpenClaw AI 助手零基础安装指南</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/11/openclaw-install-guide/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/11/openclaw-install-guide/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="✨-什么是-OpenClaw？"><a href="#✨-什么是-OpenClaw？" class="headerlink" title="✨ 什么是 OpenClaw？"></a>✨ 什么是 OpenClaw？</h2><p>OpenClaw 是一个强大的 AI 智能体框架，让你能够：</p><ul><li>🤖 创建和管理自己的 AI 助手</li><li>💬 无缝连接 Telegram、Discord、WhatsApp 等聊天平台</li><li>🔍 联网搜索、浏览器操作、文件管理等能力</li><li>🎨 自定义技能扩展，打造专属 AI 工作流</li></ul><hr><h2 id="📋-准备工作"><a href="#📋-准备工作" class="headerlink" title="📋 准备工作"></a>📋 准备工作</h2><h3 id="系统要求"><a href="#系统要求" class="headerlink" title="系统要求"></a>系统要求</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">✅ Node.js <span class="token number">22</span>+ ✅ macOS / Linux / Windows✅ 至少 4GB 内存（建议 8GB+）<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="检查版本"><a href="#检查版本" class="headerlink" title="检查版本"></a>检查版本</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">node</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--version</span>  <span class="token comment"># 应该显示 v22.0.0 或更高</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--version</span>   <span class="token comment"># 确认 npm 已安装</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><h2 id="🚀-快速安装（3-步搞定！）"><a href="#🚀-快速安装（3-步搞定！）" class="headerlink" title="🚀 快速安装（3 步搞定！）"></a>🚀 快速安装（3 步搞定！）</h2><h3 id="Step-1️⃣：一键安装脚本"><a href="#Step-1️⃣：一键安装脚本" class="headerlink" title="Step 1️⃣：一键安装脚本"></a>Step 1️⃣：一键安装脚本</h3><p><strong>macOS&#x2F;Linux 用户：</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">curl</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-fsSL</span> https://openclaw.ai/install.sh <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token function">bash</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>Windows 用户：</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-powershell" data-language="powershell"><code class="language-powershell"><span class="token function">iwr</span> <span class="token operator">-</span>useb https:<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">/</span>openclaw<span class="token punctuation">.</span>ai/install<span class="token punctuation">.</span>ps1 <span class="token punctuation">|</span> <span class="token function">iex</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>💡 安装过程会自动配置环境变量和依赖，耐心等待完成！</p></blockquote><hr><h3 id="Step-2️⃣：运行向导程序"><a href="#Step-2️⃣：运行向导程序" class="headerlink" title="Step 2️⃣：运行向导程序"></a>Step 2️⃣：运行向导程序</h3><p>安装完成后，执行以下命令启动配置向导：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">openclaw onboard --install-daemon<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>此时会出现交互式界面，引导你设置：</p><ul><li>🔐 认证配置</li><li>🌐 Gateway 服务设置</li><li>📱 可选的聊天渠道（Telegram&#x2F;微信等）</li></ul><p>跟随提示一步步操作即可！✅</p><hr><h3 id="Step-3️⃣：验证安装成功"><a href="#Step-3️⃣：验证安装成功" class="headerlink" title="Step 3️⃣：验证安装成功"></a>Step 3️⃣：验证安装成功</h3><p>检查 Gateway 状态：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">openclaw gateway status<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>打开控制面板：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">openclaw dashboard<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>如果控制界面正常加载，恭喜你！🎉 <strong>OpenClaw 已成功运行！</strong></p><hr><h2 id="🔧-进阶设置（可选）"><a href="#🔧-进阶设置（可选）" class="headerlink" title="🔧 进阶设置（可选）"></a>🔧 进阶设置（可选）</h2><h3 id="前台运行-Gateway（调试用）"><a href="#前台运行-Gateway（调试用）" class="headerlink" title="前台运行 Gateway（调试用）"></a>前台运行 Gateway（调试用）</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">openclaw gateway <span class="token parameter variable">--port</span> <span class="token number">18789</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="发送测试消息"><a href="#发送测试消息" class="headerlink" title="发送测试消息"></a>发送测试消息</h3><p>需要先配置聊天渠道：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">openclaw message send <span class="token punctuation">\</span>  <span class="token parameter variable">--target</span> +15555550123 <span class="token punctuation">\</span>  <span class="token parameter variable">--message</span> <span class="token string">"Hello from OpenClaw"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><h2 id="💡-常用命令速查"><a href="#💡-常用命令速查" class="headerlink" title="💡 常用命令速查"></a>💡 常用命令速查</h2><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>功能</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>openclaw gateway status</code></td><td>检查服务状态</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw dashboard</code></td><td>打开控制面板</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw message send</code></td><td>发送消息</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw help</code></td><td>查看帮助</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="🌟-接下来做什么？"><a href="#🌟-接下来做什么？" class="headerlink" title="🌟 接下来做什么？"></a>🌟 接下来做什么？</h2><p>完成基础安装后，你可以探索：</p><ul><li>🔗 连接更多聊天渠道（Telegram、Discord 等）</li><li>🛠️ 学习创建自定义技能（skills）</li><li>🤖 部署自己的 AI Agent</li><li>📚 查看完整文档：<a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/">https://docs.openclaw.ai</a></li></ul><hr><h2 id="❓-遇到问题？"><a href="#❓-遇到问题？" class="headerlink" title="❓ 遇到问题？"></a>❓ 遇到问题？</h2><ul><li>🐛 官方 GitHub：<a href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw">https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw</a></li><li>📖 完整文档：<a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/">https://docs.openclaw.ai</a></li><li>💬 Discord 社区：<a href="https://discord.com/invite/clawd">https://discord.com/invite/clawd</a></li></ul><hr><h2 id="🎉-结语"><a href="#🎉-结语" class="headerlink" title="🎉 结语"></a>🎉 结语</h2><p>至此，你已经成功拥有了自己的 AI 智能体框架！OpenClaw 的强大之处还远不止这些，欢迎继续探索更多功能和技能扩展～</p><hr><p><em>本文档基于官方开源项目整理，如有更新请以官方文档为准。</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
